summary: This document is an Instagram business record for the account 'ghislainemaxwell6', generated for law enforcement. It details the account's creation, associated phone number, and confirms no NCMEC cybertip reports were found for it during the specified period. The record is part of the evidence in the Ghislaine Maxwell case.

events.title: NCMEC Report Period
events.description: The period for which the Instagram account was checked for NCMEC cybertip reports; no responsive records were located.

keyFacts: An Instagram account under the username 'ghislainemaxwell6' was registered to Ghislaine Maxwell on August 14, 2019.
The account was associated with a verified U.S. phone number: +1 917 520 3106.

Law enforcement requested and received business records for this account, specifically checking for any NCMEC (National Center for Missing & Exploited Children) cybertip reports between March and June 2020; none were found.
The document is part of the evidence file (SDNY_GM_00004777, etc.) in the Southern District of New York's case against Ghislaine Maxwell.
